  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>点这里关注→</span> <span>2026-04-10 08:31</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">上海</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31716ab8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FFjoOAxHlyhwHdplTQaJBhwPyZeicGyo2H88Svr1SS8mVjPXRlljLovfBYzx8mFlldNolzrIQIIAY2wYUQrRqoXbCZ9Nk5sthke1h2lmrWXU8%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>如题</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"1036\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/FjoOAxHlyhw7gsDM5wRPsibBrwyBzT1oXbtq5lRFryyU6bjibsnKLQicpQad6xIiaUBytQHeMGAmibntQhg5WeW1f41S6NaSU7FKNdqVhjDgibMoY/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"1036\" data-imgfileid=\"504299193\" data-ratio=\"1.7916666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"768\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=30511e88&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FFjoOAxHlyhw7gsDM5wRPsibBrwyBzT1oXbtq5lRFryyU6bjibsnKLQicpQad6xIiaUBytQHeMGAmibntQhg5WeW1f41S6NaSU7FKNdqVhjDgibMoY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mn4edexv11ja\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"display: flex;flex-direction: column;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-self: flex-start;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;align-self: center;z-index: 1;width: 80px;height: 60px;margin: 0 0 -15px 0;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.506993006993007\" data-w=\"286\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=11c4a080&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FVwaIJp80uug4IfOOz8QDT8hlhwrxRjonkLYs9zAzodxhicEqQFaVRO6RZJ6pjx3x9752hoicFhHlmld2znUIqmSA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     <div style=\"background: #F0F7FE;border-radius: 4px;border: 1px solid #DAECFF;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding: 6px 18px 5px 18px;background: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=623c16c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FafC6kDohbhIdNBah7VL2q1cRI81l6slQ0xLxLN7CutaqiaU2W4yb3icsd9mWCHSnb2RD7rzL5jAlOWljfDicFSNpQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg&quot;);background-repeat: repeat;background-size: 7px 7px;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <p yb-mpa-mark=\"mark-style-text\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;color: #265BE5;line-height: 25px;word-break: break-word;\" data-mid=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">第一篇：</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">“一定要把个人的能力沉淀成组织的能力。”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span data-eleid=\"11\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">【小师妹解读】</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大家发现没？以前我们听“沉淀”觉得是褒义，是公司管理规范；但换成“蒸馏”，心里的危机感瞬间就起来了。山东那个离职员工被“数字孪生”的新闻，其实撕开了职场残酷的一面：AI 正在把过去极难复制的 SOP、工具包，变成秒级生成的生产力。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">润总提到他在微软时写的 11 篇 KB（知识库）文章，只是微软 10 万篇知识库里的冰山一角。这就是 认知差 ：所谓的“沉淀”，本质上就是把个人的归属权转移给组织。如果你的价值只在于“经验总结”，那么在 AI 时代，这种能力被“蒸馏”提取几乎是必然的。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mn4ee6svgd9\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"display: flex;flex-direction: column;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-self: flex-start;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;align-self: center;z-index: 1;width: 80px;height: 60px;margin: 0 0 -15px 0;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.506993006993007\" data-w=\"286\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=11c4a080&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FVwaIJp80uug4IfOOz8QDT8hlhwrxRjonkLYs9zAzodxhicEqQFaVRO6RZJ6pjx3x9752hoicFhHlmld2znUIqmSA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     <div style=\"background: #F0F7FE;border-radius: 4px;border: 1px solid #DAECFF;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding: 6px 18px 5px 18px;background: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=623c16c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FafC6kDohbhIdNBah7VL2q1cRI81l6slQ0xLxLN7CutaqiaU2W4yb3icsd9mWCHSnb2RD7rzL5jAlOWljfDicFSNpQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg&quot;);background-repeat: repeat;background-size: 7px 7px;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <p yb-mpa-mark=\"mark-style-text\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;color: #265BE5;line-height: 25px;word-break: break-word;\" data-mid=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">第二篇：</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <span data-eleid=\"15\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">“我们从体力工作者变成脑力工作者，未来一定会变成判断力工作者。”</span></span></span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"27\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">【小师妹解读】</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-eleid=\"31\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这是润总给所有职场人的一颗定心丸。过去我们觉得写代码、做财务、写文章是硬技能，但今天这些“脑力”正在被大规模工业化。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-eleid=\"31\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">真正的</span></span></span></span><span data-eleid=\"33\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">信息差</span></span></span></span><span data-eleid=\"35\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在于：大部分人其实是在吸收别人的技能，而只有极少数人在产生“判断”。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-eleid=\"37\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">什么是判断力？它是那种无法被轻易从你身上拿走的东西。当 7000 名工程师都能查阅 10 万篇知识库时，能在电话接通的一瞬间，从海量信息中精准锁定那个根本原因（Root Cause）并给出解决方案的人，才是不可替代的。这种锐利的判断，就是我们未来的活法。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mn4ef1c823ab\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"display: flex;flex-direction: column;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-self: flex-start;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;align-self: center;z-index: 1;width: 80px;height: 60px;margin: 0 0 -15px 0;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.506993006993007\" data-w=\"286\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=11c4a080&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FVwaIJp80uug4IfOOz8QDT8hlhwrxRjonkLYs9zAzodxhicEqQFaVRO6RZJ6pjx3x9752hoicFhHlmld2znUIqmSA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     <div style=\"background: #F0F7FE;border-radius: 4px;border: 1px solid #DAECFF;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding: 6px 18px 5px 18px;background: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=623c16c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FafC6kDohbhIdNBah7VL2q1cRI81l6slQ0xLxLN7CutaqiaU2W4yb3icsd9mWCHSnb2RD7rzL5jAlOWljfDicFSNpQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg&quot;);background-repeat: repeat;background-size: 7px 7px;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <p yb-mpa-mark=\"mark-style-text\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;color: #265BE5;line-height: 25px;word-break: break-word;\" data-mid=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">第三篇：</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">“AI会给出5个答案，到底你选哪个答案，这件事儿就是你的判断力了。”</span></span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"49\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">【小师妹解读】</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"53\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">润总提到了一个非常有画面感的场景：面对 5 个甚至 7 个选项，你选哪一个？这就是审美，这就是决策。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span data-eleid=\"55\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">认知差</span></span></span></span><span data-eleid=\"57\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在于：未来不再缺答案，而是缺“定见”。</span></span></span></span><span data-eleid=\"59\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI 可以通过算法模拟出无数种可能，但它无法承担“选错”的后果，也没有“主观”的审美倾向。正如润总提到的写作，主笔们能吸收技巧，却很难吸收那个决定文章“灵魂”的瞬间。在这个充满噪音的时代，你的审美偏好、你的风险承担、你对那个“唯一答案”的坚持，就是你最坚固的护城河。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_common_product_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-product data-windowproduct=\"v1=HE80gyPr-wG-bdzUMpJfmYrJAh18EkM8_pTNo0unJhSsxkAM2VB252X8t7CBMZ2v3cWxhg\" data-cardtype=\"1\" data-title=\"刘润·进化岛商业付费社群\" data-type=\"0\"></mp-common-product></p>\n  <div>\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0em;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-size-adjust: auto;text-align: start;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <div style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-size-adjust: auto;text-align: start;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\">\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"4 22 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-powered-by&quot;:&quot;yiban.io&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0em;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-size-adjust: auto;text-align: start;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagNam